### Pattern to Avoid (Zustand)

**❌ NEVER do this:**
```tsx
// Creates new object/array every render
const value = useStore((state) => state.data || {});
const items = useStore((state) => state.items || []);
```

**✅ ALWAYS do this:**
```tsx
// Stable selector, fallback outside
const value = useStore((state) => state.data) || {};
const items = useStore((state) => state.items) || [];

// OR for complex selectors, use useCallback
const selector = useCallback((state) => state.data || {}, []);
const value = useStore(selector);
```

